workflowStepDefs.name: Prep Reagents
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Before starting, confirm all reagents have been prepared: Buffer AL incubated at 56C to dissolve precipitate, if needed 100% Ethanol added to Buffer AW1 100% Ethanol added to Buffer AW2

workflowStepDefs.name: Prep workspace
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Disinfect lab space and sample rack.

workflowStepDefs.name: Incubate Samples
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Collect samples for extraction from +4°C fridge or freezer. If samples are frozen, incubate at 37°C for 10 minutes. Remove from incubator and place on ice.

workflowStepDefs.name: Transfer to microcentrifuge tube
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Label one microcentrifuge tube for each sample. Pipet 20ul of proteinase K into the tube. Add 200ul of blood to each microcentrifuge tube. Add 200ul of Buffer AL to each microcentrifuge tube.

workflowStepDefs.name: Mix AL
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Mix by pulse vortexing for 15 seconds.

workflowStepDefs.name: Incubate AL
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Incubate at 56°C for 10 minutes.

workflowStepDefs.name: Centrifuge AL
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Briefly centrifuge the tube to remove drops from the lid.

workflowStepDefs.name: Add Ethanol
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Add 200ul of 100% ethanol to the sample.

workflowStepDefs.name: Mix Ethanol
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Mix by pulse vortexing for 15 seconds.

workflowStepDefs.name: Transfer to spin column
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Apply the mixture to the QIAamp Mini spin column in a 2ml collection tube

workflowStepDefs.name: Centrifuge Ethanol
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Spin at 6000 x g for 1 minute.

workflowStepDefs.name: Move Column After Ethanol
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Place the column in a clean 2ml collection tube and discard the tube with the filtrate.

workflowStepDefs.name: Add AW1
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Add 500ul Buffer AW1 to the column.

workflowStepDefs.name: Centrifuge AW1
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Spin at 6,000 x g for 1 minute.

workflowStepDefs.name: Move Column After AW1
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Place the column in a clean 2ml collection tube and discard the tube with the filtrate.

workflowStepDefs.name: Add AW2
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Add 500ul Buffer AW2 to the column.

workflowStepDefs.name: Centrifuge AW2
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Spin at full speed (20,000 x g) for 3 minutes.

workflowStepDefs.name: Move Column After AW2
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Place the column in a clean 2ml collection tube and discard the tube with the filtrate.

workflowStepDefs.name: Second Centrifuge After AW2
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Spin at full speed for 1 minute.

workflowStepDefs.name: Second Move Column After AW2
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Place the column in a clean 1.5ml microcentrifuge tube and discard the tube with the filtrate.

workflowStepDefs.name: Add AE
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Add 200ul Buffer AE to the column and incubate at room temperature for 1 minute.

workflowStepDefs.name: Centrifuge AE
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Spin at 6,000 x g for 1 minute.

workflowStepDefs.name: Transfer to matrix
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Transfer the eluate to a labeled 0.5ml barcoded 2D matrix tube.

workflowStepDefs.name: Store
workflowStepDefs.instructions: If necessary, store at +4°C until ready to proceed to Plating.
